<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "S8T40A4106001" svcinfotypenbr = "08" svcinfoqualnbr = "03" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Excessive Pedal Travel Check
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Start engine.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Depress brake pedal a few times.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
When brake pedal depressed, measure brake pedal to carpet clearance &#8220;c&#8221;.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
There are possibilities of the following causes.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Rear brake shoe is worn out beyond limit. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A4326004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Air is in brake lines. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A4106004"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
If measured clearance &#8220;c&#8221; is less than specification even after replacement of brake shoes and bleeding of system, there are possibilities of the following causes.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Malfunction of rear brake shoe adjuster. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A4326006"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Booster push rod length out of adjustment. 
<intxreftitleoff1 refid = "S8T40A4106019"><img src = "..\icon\intxreftitleoff.gif"/></intxreftitleoff1>
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</s1>
<spec-sdm>
<sdm-title>
Brake pedal to wall clearance
</sdm-title>
<sdm-part>
&#8220;c&#8221;
</sdm-part>
<sdm1>
<sdm-condition>
When pedal depressed at 300 N (30.6 kgf, 67.5 lbf)
</sdm-condition>
<sdm-value>
Over 80 mm (3.15 in.)
</sdm-value>
</sdm1>
</spec-sdm>
